247
00:25:07,550 --> 00:25:09,510
Perhaps later I could show you-
Jordan.

248
00:25:09,670 --> 00:25:12,090
What?
-Exercise 73, remember?

249
00:25:12,260 --> 00:25:14,880
Yeah, they tell me 73's the charm.

250
00:25:15,050 --> 00:25:17,050
Good day, Miss Ferris.

251
00:25:22,010 --> 00:25:23,880
