268
00:27:04,880 --> 00:27:06,260
His name's Faraday.

269
00:27:06,420 --> 00:27:08,630
Works for the government.

270
00:27:08,970 --> 00:27:11,880
And if you like Rick Flagg,
you'll love him.

271
00:27:13,630 --> 00:27:16,050
You're weak, erratic, emotional...

272
00:27:16,220 --> 00:27:20,460
...and for my money, at least a little pink.
But I'm told you're the best we've got.

273
00:27:21,970 --> 00:27:23,590
I...
-You keep your mouth shut...

274
00:27:23,930 --> 00:27:25,050
...and your ears open.

275
00:27:25,220 --> 00:27:28,510
