280
00:27:50,760 --> 00:27:54,050
Yes, Jordan, I'm a real kidder.

281
00:27:54,720 --> 00:27:57,510
We found this footprint
at the observatory.

282
00:27:58,930 --> 00:28:01,340
Did you find what made that print?

283
00:28:01,510 --> 00:28:02,590
No.

284
00:28:03,050 --> 00:28:06,630
Whatever it is,
it's eluded us for two years.

285
00:28:07,050 --> 00:28:09,090
There's life on Mars, Jordan.

286
00:28:09,260 --> 00:28:10,970
And it's come to Earth.

287
00:28:12,010 --> 00:28:14,970
