What does this have to do with me?

288
00:28:23,380 --> 00:28:25,300
You haven't figured it out yet?

289
00:28:25,970 --> 00:28:28,380
We've got to know what these Martians
want from us...

290
00:28:28,550 --> 00:28:31,220
...and since we can't find them
here on Earth...

291
00:28:31,720 --> 00:28:33,140
...we're going to Mars.

292
00:28:37,630 --> 00:28:39,550
Outstanding.

293
00:28:48,420 --> 00:28:50,590
